trans-unit.source: An object that supports the control pattern if <paramref name="patternInterface" /> is the <see cref="F:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.PatternInterface.Scroll" />, <see cref="F:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.PatternInterface.ItemContainer" />, <see cref="F:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.PatternInterface.SynchronizedInput" /> value, or if the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.Ribbon.RibbonQuickAccessToolBar" /> has items in the overflow menu and <paramref name="patternInterface" /> is the <see cref="F:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.PatternInterface.ExpandCollapse" /> value; otherwise, <see langword="null" />.
trans-unit.target: Ein Objekt, von dem das Steuerelementmuster unterstützt wird, wenn <paramref name="patternInterface" /> den Wert <see cref="F:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.PatternInterface.Scroll" />, <see cref="F:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.PatternInterface.ItemContainer" />, <see cref="F:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.PatternInterface.SynchronizedInput" /> hat oder wenn <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.Ribbon.RibbonQuickAccessToolBar" /> Elemente im Überlaufmenü aufweist und <paramref name="patternInterface" /> den Wert <see cref="F:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.PatternInterface.ExpandCollapse" /> hat, andernfalls <see langword="null" />.
